definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to artisans or the work of artisans.
Involving skilled work, with comparatively little reliance on machinery.

definitions.label_groups: of an item, especially a foodstuff

main_definition: Of or pertaining to artisans or the work of artisans.
secondary_definitions: Involving skilled work, with comparatively little reliance on machinery.
( of an item, especially a foodstuff ) Made by an artisan (skilled worker).
